⭐ What is a Custom Widget?

A custom widget is your own widget created by combining Flutter widgets (Container, Row, Text, etc.) so it can be reused anywhere.

tyeps:
Stateless Custom Widget

Stateful Custom Widget

| Feature           | StatelessWidget | StatefulWidget               |
| ----------------- | --------------- | ---------------------------- |
| UI changes        | ❌ No            | ✔ Yes                        |
| setState()        | ❌ Not used      | ✔ Used                       |
| Stores state/data | ❌ No            | ✔ Yes                        |
| Lifecycle         | Simple          | Complex (initState, dispose) |
| Performance       | Faster          | Slightly slower              |
| Good for          | Static UI       | Dynamic UI                   |
